programme.desc: Rohana desak Fariz agar berkahwin dengan Rania. Bagaimanapun Fariz menolaknya dan bertegas walau apa cara sekalipun, dia akan tetap berkahwin dengan Ainnura. programme.title: Mister Mayfair - Serenas Game
programme.desc: Refusing to comply with Tommys demands, Max and Paul conspire to have the British gangster eliminated and Serena arrested. With Tommy dead and Serena in handcuffs, it appears as though Max has succeeded. His plan goes awry, however, when MI6 force Max to help Serena bring down her employers: the Russian mob. Torn between a life of crime with Serena or happiness with Ava, nothing is ever simple in the life of Max Mayfair.

programme.title: In Isolation
programme.desc: Four friends wanted to get away from it all in a remote country house but when a mysterious injured man turns up on their doorstep telling tales of a city ravaged by a epidemic and the looters who have pursued him, the friends rally to help.

programme.title: Hideout
programme.desc: Evading police at a remote farmhouse after fumbling a robbery, four criminals discover that the family living there is not who they appear to be.

programme.title: Broken Star
programme.desc: Abandoned by her friends and family and with her career in jeopardy, starlet Markey Marlowe is sequestered in a duplex with a reclusive landlord who just may be more dangerous than she is.

programme.title: A Tale Of Two Guns
programme.desc: A deputized gunslinger takes up the call to hunt down the last Cowboy, the chase is on and the bullets fly and only one of these hardened men can survive.

programme.title: The Legion
programme.desc: Noreno, a half-Roman, is entrusted with the mission of crossing the snowy mountains of Armenia, swarming with Parthian patrols, to seek help for his slowly dying men.

programme.title: Altitude
programme.desc: A female FBI agent is offered millions to help a thief escape from a hijacked airplane.

programme.title: Heartbreakers
programme.desc: Max and Page, a brilliant mother-daughter swindler team, target the citys wealthiest men. Max marries them and then sues for alimony after she catches them involved in an affair with Page.

programme.title: Escape Through Africa
programme.desc: Following a violent raid on her outpost, a British nurse, Anne is on the run with a small group of soldiers. She must balance bravery with compassion to save a native girl, her husband, and her colony.

programme.title: Mister Mayfair - A Song To Kill For
programme.desc: Max Mayfair has it all; a beautiful girlfriend, Ava, a new London crime family, and thanks to his latest heist, a priceless diamond necklace. However, when mafioso Calbones henchmen catch up with Mike and Armen, determined to drag them back to New York to pay for their crimes, Max has everything to lose. Teaming up with his old friend, Marseille Mafia crime boss, Paul, Max hatches a plan to lure the New York Mafia to Mayfair.

programme.title: Override
programme.desc: In 2040, a female humanoid A.I. is hacked by her husband and forced to kidnap the U.S. vice presidents son and execute him on live television.

programme.title: Chosen
programme.desc: The Jews of Eastern Europe are being massacred by the thousands. Galvanised into action after the death of his wife, Hungarian barrister Sonson finds himself leading an inspirational fight back against the increasingly desperate and dangerous Nazis.

programme.title: Project Legion
programme.desc: A young man trapped in his apartment with a swarm of demons outside his door must find a way to survive the night and escape from apartment 213.

programme.title: Blowback
programme.desc: After planning a perfect heist, Nick is ready to score. One problem, his girl and the crew, have other ideas. They take Nick down in a hail of bullets but Nick doesnt die and in a race for his life, seeks revenge one target at a time.

programme.title: Crom
programme.desc: High school teenagers accidentally unleash an ancient Irish entity on their hometown and must stop it before midnight on Halloween.

programme.title: Clean
programme.desc: Tormented by his criminal past, Clean attempts a quiet life caring for his community and as a mentor to his young neighbor Dianda. When local gang violence puts his neighbors life in danger, Clean finds himself returning to his violent past.

programme.title: Johnny And Clyde
programme.desc: Johnny and Clyde are two serial killers who are on an endless crime spree. They decide to assemble a group of criminals and misfits to steal from Alanas casino and pull off the heist of the century.

programme.title: Blindfire
programme.desc: A police officer who while responding to a violent hostage call, kills the African American suspect only to later learn of his innocence. Sensing this was a set-up, and facing repercussions, he must track down the person responsible while examining his own accountability and the ingrained racism which brought him to this point.

programme.title: The Commando
programme.desc: A DEA agent returns home with PTSD after a botched mission and must now protect his family from a home invasion when a recently freed convict and his henchmen come after their stash of millions hidden inside of the agents home.

programme.title: Pocket Listing
programme.desc: Double crosses, adultery, murder, mistaken identity, and revenge ensue when a mysterious power player and his sultry wife hire a disgraced Los Angeles property broker to discreetly market and sell their Malibu villa.

programme.title: Blood Of Redemption

programme.title: High Voltage
programme.desc: After a lightning strike kills the lead singer of a band, she is resurrected with electrifying special abilities.

programme.desc: Brother Hui, who runs an amphibian and reptile store in Xinxing District, Kaohsiung City, has a wide range of knowledge in the field of reptiles. In Brother Huis brick-and-mortar store, the most special existence is the two store pets, the South American lizards. The male is called Meatball and the female is called Porkball. programme.title: Te Tengo en Salsa - S01:E20
programme.desc: Al percatarse que ha dejado su celular en una tienda, Adriana se aleja de Tatiana y Patricia; justo entonces, esta se topa con Cesar Romn, quien la reconoce de inmediato.

programme.title: La Trepadora - S01:E113
programme.desc: Justo cuando Victoria le impide a Sergio anunciar su compromiso frente a la familia Guanipa, Sergio cree que la mujer se arrepintio; Victoria es quien anuncia su matrimonio, lo que sorprende a todos. Adelaida en compaa de Hansen, recuerda la niez de su hija Victoria, quien desde pequea ha sido traviesa; la sensacion de tener a su hija en peligro y no poder hacer nada desperto en ella un sentimiento ms grande. Victoria evita los besos de Sergio, quien se apresura por ponerle fecha a su matrimonio; Sergio ya ha preparado todo para casarse en una semana.

programme.title: La Trepadora - S01:E114
programme.desc: Ante la insistencia de Sergio por apresurar la boda, Victoria trata de convencerlo de esperar un tiempo, pero no tiene motivos para no adelantar su boda, as que Victoria acepta casarse en una semana. A escondidas, Nicols escucha cuando Florencia le advierte a Fernanda so miedo de perder a su esposo, porque si no fuera por la trampa que ambas fraguaron ya Nicols la hubiese abandonado; un indignado Nicols las enfrenta, pues no puede creer que su ta y su esposa lo hayan engaado para impedir su matrimonio con Victoria. A solas con su esposa, Nicols entiende como Florencia lo vio sufrir por Victoria y an as lo traiciono, as que Nicols decide separarse de ella; Florencia no quiere ser condenada por un error, pero Nicols admite que su error es haberse casado con ella. El miedo embarga a Victoria por su nueva vida junto a su futuro esposo, Sergio, pero Adelaida apoya la decision de su hija; En un nuevo da, cuando Victoria le afirma a su madre que siente una necesidad de huir de sus sentimientos por Nicols, Adelaida se le impone, pues no apoyar a su hija en la decision de casarse, pues le aconseja hablar con Sergio y cancelar el matrimonio.

programme.title: Piel Salvaje - S01:E03

programme.title: Corazon Traicionado - S01:E23
programme.desc: Gertrudis reminds Claudio of the convenience of keeping their relationship hidden to avoid raising suspicions while living the freedom of their love. programme.desc: Manny tangles with a monster hog in the dense woods of Port Labelle.

programme.title: Savage Wild - S05:E08 - Save a Watermelon Kill a Boar Part 1
programme.desc: Manny tracks down a boar raiding watermelon fields in southwestern Florida.

programme.title: Savage Wild - S05:E09 - Save a Watermelon Kill a Boar Part 2
programme.desc: After slaying a monster boar, Manny heads back into the forest and goes toe to toe with an even bigger boar.

programme.title: Savage Wild - S05:E10 - How to Stop a Charging Wild Boar
programme.desc: In this episode of Savage Wild, were headed into the palmettos with Full Rut Outfitters in search of wild boar.

programme.title: Miracles of Nature - S01:E07 - Naturally Majestic
programme.desc: Follow in the footsteps of Indiana Jones. In this episode of Miracles of Nature we visit the wonders of the Gobi Desert which is one of the oldest deserts in the world, and then the contrasting lush, green hillsides of northern Mongolian. From there we travel 5000 kilometres to the south east to Jordan and the Dead Sea.

programme.title: Miracles of Nature - S01:E08 - Naturally Raw
programme.desc: This episode begins in Costa Rica, in an amazing rain forest. Here they make delicious chocolate out of cocoa beans. Mother Nature is at her magnificent best showcasing hundreds of plant and animal species. And then to Kenya where green monkeys will be our tour-guides in the Lost City of Gedi plus a closer look at the wildlife which lives in very close proximity to the bustling streets of Nairobi.

programme.title: Miracles of Nature - S01:E09 - Naturally Invigorating
programme.desc: Iceland: home to volcanic lakes and hot springs and mono-chromatic vistas. And then to Laos in South East Asia with its lush jungles, underground caves and water buffalo along the Mekong River.

programme.title: Miracles of Nature - S01:E10 - Naturally Potent
programme.desc: Explore the unspoilt mountains of Lapland and on to the pristine Swiss Alps. In contrast we then travel to Champagne Province in France - home of the finest wines in the world. Finally, Gibraltar beckons with its long history and strange mysterious caves.

programme.title: Savage Wild - S05:E07 - Slaying the Port Labelle Monster
programme.desc: Manny tangles with a monster hog in the dense woods of Port Labelle.

programme.title: Carters W.A.R. - S01:E01 - Rhino Wars
programme.desc: Carters W.A.R. (Wild Animal Response) is the untold story of one mans quest to save his homeland, the worlds most wild and dangerous continent on earth, Africa. From heavily armed poachers butchering elephants for their tusks to the slaughter of rhinos for their horns, Africas most precious resource is in peril. Can one man expose the truth and make a difference? Watch as wildlife detective and professional hunter, Ivan Carter, takes you inside the real Africa to the front lines of the wars being waged on its wildlife. In this episode Ivan Carter exposes the secret war in Africa. A war of greed thats putting the rhino in danger.

programme.title: Carters W.A.R. - S01:E02 - White Gold
programme.desc: Ivan Carter works to save a key elephant from ivory poachers near Africas famous Kruger National Park.

programme.title: Carters W.A.R. - S01:E03 - Death in the Water
programme.desc: Ivan Carter reveals Africas hard choices as he investigates a reported man killing a hippo.

programme.title: Carters W.A.R. - S01:E04 - No Win Scenario
programme.desc: Ivan Carter investigates a tragic croc attack on Africas Zambezi River.

programme.title: Carters W.A.R. - S01:E05 - Gang Wars
